text: The spotjaw moray (Gymnothorax mareei) is a moray eel found in the eastern Atlantic Ocean.Gymnothorax mareei at www.fishbase.org. It was first named by Max Poll in 1953.Common names for Spot-jaw moray at www.fishbase.org. ==References== mareei Category:Fish described in 1953
